videos.description: Anthony Brown finds Jake Burt for a 3-yard touchdown to open the scoring for Boston College.
videos.headline: Burt hauls in 3-yard TD

videos.description: Eric Dungey finds a wide-open Sean Riley for a 75-yard touchdown to tie Boston College at 7.
videos.headline: Syracuse's Dungey finds wide-open Riley for long TD

videos.description: Syracuse's Eric Dungey finds the edge and scores on a 4-yard run.
videos.headline: Eric Dungey scampers for 4-yard TD

videos.description: Eric Dungey fakes a handoff and runs the bootleg for a 2-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Eric Dungey scores on 2-yard bootleg

videos.description: Anthony Brown fires a deep 69-yard touchdown to Jeff Smith to cut the deficit to 21-14.
videos.headline: BC's Smith uncovered on 69-yard TD

videos.description: Eric Dungey runs for an 18-yard touchdown, his third of the day and 35th for his career.
videos.headline: Syracuse's Dungey dashes for 3rd rushing TD

videos.description: Ben Glines catches a 29-yard touchdown pass from Anthony Brown.
videos.headline: Eagles' Brown finds Glines for 29-yard TD

videos.description: Jamal Custis snags a 22-yard touchdown pass from Eric Dungey.
videos.headline: Cuse's Custis hauls in 22-yard TD
